{"tid":1740390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實黎明行動塞鐵唔洗多人 需要既係令人厭惡既野","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T04:12:55.000Z","uid":74821,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"907f835975043b09922904e0a325c74797221b46","tid":1740390,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊叔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你班𡃁仔咁塞法實比人嘈啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 無計啦，全因個仆街政府囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 實係㗎啦，其實洗鬼花咁多人力物力去塞鐵咩，每個站揾幾個人掉啲臭野落架車廂，愈臭愈好，掉完就走，太臭啲人係自然唔會上車啦 掉完可以去做其他野嘛 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（千祈唔好玩臭魚同屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"74e752200cf23b269993f181fc2b0259d106cda5","tid":1740390,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得勇武暫時要休息，咁作為和理非嘅你請今晚出場，今晚有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"061d2689f902f893c1a0275600dd19b327db0061","tid":1740390,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:19:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b864495c76aecdef0ec56e0c4549b1c3f866422","tid":1740390,"uid":283700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"由於近日多個交通燈被破壞，碎石滿地，危險滿佈，現呼籲各道路使用者以p牌的心態駕駛，即以低速行駛，跟住別人駕駛，小心行駛，以安全保命為首要，路口出大路則應互相禮讓，共創美好道路，目標開心駕駛零意外。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗太故意去做，我相信咁多人唔係得幾個有車既，人地想爬頭就比人爬，自己安全要緊，最後希望唔洗番工或番晏既可以早上一齊練下車"},{"pid":"e39d21a96c2c6819c83139c739fa809119a28824","tid":1740390,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba35820f3c21ab825ca96bf006d8c6ed11753e6a","tid":1740390,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"食完八寶粥暈車浪嘔出黎<br />\n大家都唔想"},{"pid":"6b123d53c4b98b70f09ed747d4e82293f8fa1bef","tid":1740390,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e303ce04e915825d5f63df76aeff3a0833538934","tid":1740390,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba35820f3c21ab825ca96bf006d8c6ed11753e6a","tid":1740390,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"食完八寶粥暈車浪嘔出黎<br />\n大家都唔想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"咁仲好 幫塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa90889ca96c2899aa1f4d9d0628264b6c60d5e","tid":1740390,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b864495c76aecdef0ec56e0c4549b1c3f866422","tid":1740390,"uid":283700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"由於近日多個交通燈被破壞，碎石滿地，危險滿佈，現呼籲各道路使用者以p牌的心態駕駛，即以低速行駛，跟住別人駕駛，小心行駛，以安全保命為首要，路口出大路則應互相禮讓，共創美好道路，目標開心駕駛零意外。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗太故意去做，我相信咁多人唔係得幾個有車既，人地想爬頭就比人爬，自己安全要緊，最後希望唔洗番工或番晏既可以早上一齊練下車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128b01fcf5c2fb0953d772d2296a8d1cc914707f","tid":1740390,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會太睇少香港人對返工執著"},{"pid":"88d1c9e0a344506028547c8939b66b87905310d7","tid":1740390,"uid":50894,"like":